dataset_id: LBA-ECO LC-24 Land Cover Classes from Landsat TM, Uruara, Para: 1986-1991
title: LBA-ECO LC-24 Land Cover Classes from Landsat TM, Uruara, Para: 1986-1991
summary: This data set provides course land cover classifications derived from Landsat TM images for 1986, 1988, and 1991 for the area surrounding the municipality of Uruara, Para, Brazil. Five land cover classes (Water, Clouds/Shadow, Forest, Not Forest, and Background) were derived (Aldrich et al. 2006). The Land Cover is in a compressed (*.zip) GeoTIFF file for each year.
